{"tid":1302290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國輝寶宣布研發非洲豬瘟疫苗取得重大突破 計劃中國設廠","createTime":"2019-07-10T01:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T05:13:28.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"219bfa073da1be5087d7d4950e47b41c0ff22896","tid":1302290,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"美國輝寶動物保健公司於當地時間8日宣布，在非洲豬瘟疫苗（ASF）的研發上取得重大進展，該公司正在申請專利保護。從輝寶中國業務發展部了解到，他們考慮將組建合資公司，後續可能將非洲豬瘟疫苗的生產地設在中國。（via 一財）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190709/31900126.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190709%2F31900126.html&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Cn4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=cb47c21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20190709/31900126.html</a><br />\n<br />\n啲研究成果俾人偷硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467f98bba1c65cc3fece2dad1da0b059064a15bc","tid":1302290,"uid":55517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:53:55.000Z","msg":"咁偉大嘅發明記住賣貴啲<br />\n小心俾人偷研究成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c016d58712ad958e8d52e2ac08f65c93a3c60ed3","tid":1302290,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解中國設廠?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為中國有13億豬隻 係龐大市場 無需外銷 唔怕關稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbac6f14755caa006e6aa3a7cdf6ffcc71939cfb","tid":1302290,"uid":267950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T02:18:23.000Z","msg":"輝寶＂中國＂話＂考慮＂，＂可能＂<br />\n大６佬就是老吹<br />\nFact check 原新聞稿只不過話重大進展，其實tech天天都可以有重大進展<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/